OL,4,CMinimum unit alcohol price has 'lasting
OL,5,Cimpact'
OL,6, The introduction of minimum pricing of
OL,7, alcohol has had a lasting impact in
OL,8, Scotland and is starting to have an
OL,9, effect in Wales, a study has found.
OL,11,FResearch from Newcastle University and
OL,12,Fpublished in the Lancet found alcohol
OL,13,Fsales fell by almost 8% after the
OL,14,Fpolicy was introduced in Scotland.
OL,16,FIt became the first country in the
OL,17,Fworld to bring in minimum unit pricing
OL,18,F(MUP) for alcohol in May 2018,
OL,19,Fcurrently fixed at 50p per unit.
OL,21,FWales introduced the policy last March.
